<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Employment Offer Letter</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000;
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }
        
        .document-container {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 25mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            background: white;
        }
        
        /* Clean Professional Header */
        .letterhead {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .company-name {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .company-address {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #000;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        /* Document Header */
        .document-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .document-title {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Date and Reference */
        .date-reference {
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #000;
        }
        
        .date-line {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        /* Recipient */
        .recipient {
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .recipient-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 12pt;
        }
        
        /* Subject Line */
        .subject-line {
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        /* Main Content */
        .content {
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        /* Professional Details Table */
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 2px solid #000;
        }
        
        .details-table th,
        .details-table td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }
        
        .details-table th {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        /* Terms Section */
        .terms-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .terms-title {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .terms-list {
            list-style: decimal;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .terms-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        /* Signature Section */
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .signature-block {
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        
        .signature-title {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            padding-top: 8px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }
        
        .signature-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .document-footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        /* Print Styles */
        @media print {
            .document-container {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 20mm;
            }
            
            body {
                background: white;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="document-container">
        <!-- Professional Letterhead -->
        <div class="letterhead">
            <div class="company-name">{{companyName}}</div>
            <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
            {{#if companyPhone}}<div>Phone: {{companyPhone}} {{#if companyEmail}}| Email: {{companyEmail}}{{/if}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>

        <!-- Document Title -->
        <div class="document-header">
            <div class="document-title">Offer Letter</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Date and Reference -->
        <div class="date-reference">
            <div class="date-line"><strong>Date:</strong> {{offerDate}}</div>
            {{#if refNumber}}<div><strong>Ref No:</strong> {{refNumber}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>

        <!-- Recipient Information -->
        <div class="recipient">
            <div><strong>To,</strong></div>
            <div class="recipient-name">{{candidateName}}</div>
            {{#if candidateAddress}}<div>{{candidateAddress}}</div>{{/if}}
        </div>

        <!-- Subject -->
        <div class="subject-line">
            <strong>Subject: Offer of Employment - {{position}}</strong>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{candidateName}},</p>

            <p>We are pleased to offer you employment with {{companyName}} for the position of <strong>{{position}}</strong>. We believe your skills and experience will be valuable to our organization.</p>

            <!-- Employment Details Table -->
            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <th>Position</th>
                    <td>{{position}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Department</th>
                    <td>{{department}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Annual Salary</th>
                    <td>₹{{salary}} per annum</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Date of Joining</th>
                    <td>{{startDate}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Reporting To</th>
                    <td>{{reportingTo}}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Work Location</th>
                    <td>{{workLocation}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{#if probationPeriod}}
                <tr>
                    <th>Probation Period</th>
                    <td>{{probationPeriod}}</td>
                </tr>
                {{/if}}
            </table>

            <!-- Terms and Conditions -->
            <div class="terms-section">
                <div class="terms-title">Terms and Conditions</div>
                <ol class="terms-list">
                    <li>Your employment is subject to satisfactory completion of background verification and reference checks.</li>
                    <li>You will be governed by the company's rules, regulations, and policies as amended from time to time.</li>
                    <li>You are required to maintain strict confidentiality regarding company information and business.</li>
                    <li>This offer is contingent upon your acceptance within 7 days from the date of this letter.</li>
                    <li>Your employment will be subject to a probation period of {{#if probationPeriod}}{{probationPeriod}}{{else}}90 days{{/if}}.</li>
                    <li>Either party may terminate employment with {{#if noticePeriod}}{{noticePeriod}}{{else}}30 days{{/if}} written notice.</li>
                    <li>You will be entitled to benefits as per company policy including health insurance and paid leave.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <p>Please confirm your acceptance by signing and returning a copy of this letter. We look forward to welcoming you to our team.</p>

            <p>Congratulations and welcome to {{companyName}}!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Professional Signature Section -->
        <div class="signature-section">
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div class="signature-title">For {{companyName}}</div>
                <div class="signature-line">
                    <div class="signature-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Manager{{/if}}</div>
                    <div>Human Resources</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="signature-block">
                <div class="signature-title">Acceptance</div>
                <div class="signature-line">
                    <div class="signature-name">{{candidateName}}</div>
                    <div>Date: ___________</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="document-footer">
            <p>This is a computer-generated document.</p>
            <p>{{companyName}} - Professional HR System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>